{"tid":671043,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人生嘅意義係？(宗教哲學JJ入)","createTime":"2018-05-19T19:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T12:03:36.000Z","uid":183429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d37b11cd279ff2a7bd7fdf6be57f8947f013b4e5","tid":671043,"uid":183429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:37:35.000Z","msg":"有生就有死，有合就有離，有喜就有悲，衰老 患病 死亡 在不久將來。<br />\n     如有死後歸處，那麼出生前又謂何物？( 如非用唯物論思考， 咁有始有終 無始則無終)<br />\n     所謂的「我」或「 靈魂 」是何物？ 人出生以來， 身體所接觸之物， 皆為外物， 有何超然於物質的靈魂， 死後靈魂存在之論 何以成立？ 所有嘅心靈、思考 都係以出世以來所接觸到嘅資訊 加以分析 理解 推理， 那麼所謂的靈魂又有咩做， 有何特別...<br />\n( 應該又有好多人有入嚟話宇宙大爆炸+ 唯物論， 下刪1000字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"a701d20e62ed8ff4996103cbc03732a653da5c0a","tid":671043,"uid":183429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:39:28.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75a27967c2a73fa0ef47bc006b9a1e9ba00d620","tid":671043,"uid":183429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:41:01.000Z","msg":"睇嚟大家已經瞓著咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21366224a4ee3826e2a2004d2bb433060dc953ee","tid":671043,"uid":59711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:45:23.000Z","msg":"仲揾緊人生既意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一般人結婚生仔吃喝玩樂呢d,對我黎講唔算係人生意義"},{"pid":"8b085b9cfd594d2740b8b5b182ec37df2b591344","tid":671043,"uid":183429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21366224a4ee3826e2a2004d2bb433060dc953ee","tid":671043,"uid":59711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:45:23.000Z","msg":"仲揾緊人生既意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一般人結婚生仔吃喝玩樂呢d,